        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Open America's Waters Act</b></p> <p>This bill repeals certain limitations on the types of vessels that may engage in coastwise trade, which is the domestic transportation of merchandise or passengers by vessels. </p> <p>The bill directs the U.S. Coast Guard to issue regulations that require all vessels permitted to engage in coastwise trade to meet all appropriate safety and security requirements.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
